TITLE: Implementing Request Middleware in TypeScript for Web3.js
DESCRIPTION: Example of a request middleware class that implements RequestManagerMiddleware interface to log RPC requests and responses. The middleware can intercept and modify both requests before sending to network and responses before returning to Web3.js.
