TITLE: Setting Up Module Augmentation in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Configures module augmentation in TypeScript to enable access to the custom plugin on the Web3 object, allowing for proper type inference and autocompletion.
SOURCE: https://github.com/web3/web3.js/blob/4.x/docs/docs/guides/13_advanced/custom_RPC.md#2025-04-21_snippet_6

